51                        shareRecord.ParentId = meetingId;
52                        shareRecord.UserOrGroupId = userId;
53                        shareRecord.AccessLevel = 'Edit';
54                        shareRecordsToInsert.add(shareRecord);
55                    }
56                }
57            }
58            insert shareRecordsToInsert;
59
60        } else if (Trigger.isUpdate) {
61            
62            Map<Id, Set<Id>> meetingIdToRemovedUserIds = new Map<Id, Set<Id>>();
63            Map<Id, Set<Id>> meetingIdToNewUserIds = new Map<Id, Set<Id>>();
64
65            for (Team_Member_MERC__c m : teamMembersToProcess) {
66                Id oldMapUser = (Id)Trigger.oldmap.get(m.Id).get('User_MERC__c');
67                Id newMapUser = (Id)Trigger.newmap.get(m.Id).get('User_MERC__c');
68
69                if (oldMapUser != newMapUser) {
70                    if (oldMapUser != null) {
71                        //oldmapuser needs to be removed from share table
72                        if (meetingIdToRemovedUserIds.containsKey(m.Meeting_MERC__c)) {
73                            Set<Id> existingSet = meetingIdToRemovedUserIds.get(m.Meeting_MERC__c);
74                            existingSet.add(oldMapUser);
75                            meetingIdToRemovedUserIds.put(m.Meeting_MERC__c, existingSet);
76                        } else {
77                            Set<Id> newSet = new Set<Id>();
78                            newSet.add(oldMapUser);
79                            meetingIdToRemovedUserIds.put(m.Meeting_MERC__c, newSet);
80                        }
81                    }
82                    if (newMapUser != null) {
83                        //newmapuser needs to be added to share table
84                        if (meetingIdToNewUserIds.containsKey(m.Meeting_MERC__c)) {
85                            Set<Id> existingSet = meetingIdToNewUserIds.get(m.Meeting_MERC__c);
86                            existingSet.add(newMapUser);
87                            meetingIdToNewUserIds.put(m.Meeting_MERC__c, existingSet);
88                        } else {
89                            Set<Id> newSet = new Set<Id>();
90                            newSet.add(newMapUser);
91                            meetingIdToNewUserIds.put(m.Meeting_MERC__c, newSet);
92                        }
93                    }
94                }
95            }
96
97            if (meetingIdToRemovedUserIds.keySet().size() > 0) {
98                List<Meeting_MERC__Share> shareRecordsToDelete = new List<Meeting_MERC__Share>();
99                for (Meeting_MERC__Share share : [SELECT ID, UserOrGroupId, ParentId From Meeting_MERC__Share WHERE ParentId in :meetingIdToRemovedUserIds.keySet()]) {
100                    if (meetingIdToRemovedUserIds.get(share.ParentId) != null) {
101                        Set<Id> removedUserIds = meetingIdToRemovedUserIds.get(share.ParentId);
102                        if (removedUserIds.contains(share.UserOrGroupId)) {
103                            system.debug('DELETING FROM SHARE >>>> '+share);
104                            shareRecordsToDelete.add(share);
105                        }
106                    }
107                }
108                delete shareRecordsToDelete;
109            }
110
111            if (meetingIdToNewUserIds.keySet().size() > 0) {
112                List<Meeting_MERC__Share> shareRecordsToInsert = new List<Meeting_MERC__Share>();
113                for (Id meetingId : meetingIdToNewUserIds.keySet()) {
114                    Set<Id> userIdsToAddToShareTable = meetingIdToNewUserIds.get(meetingId);
115                    for (Id userId : userIdsToAddToShareTable) {
116                        if (userId != meetingMap.get(meetingId).OwnerId) {
117                            Meeting_MERC__Share shareRecord = new Meeting_MERC__Share();
118                            shareRecord.ParentId = meetingId;
119                            shareRecord.UserOrGroupId = userId;
120                            shareRecord.AccessLevel = 'Edit';
121                            system.debug('INSERTING TO SHARE >>>> '+shareRecord);
122
123                            shareRecordsToInsert.add(shareRecord);
124                        }
125                    }
126                }
127                insert shareRecordsToInsert;
128            }
129
130        } else if (Trigger.isDelete) {
131            Map<Id, Set<Id>> meetingIdToRemovedUserIds = getMeetingIdToTriggerUserIds(teamMembersToProcess);
132            
133            List<Meeting_MERC__Share> shareRecordsToDelete = new List<Meeting_MERC__Share>();
134            for (Meeting_MERC__Share share : [SELECT ID, UserOrGroupId, ParentId From Meeting_MERC__Share WHERE ParentId in :meetingIdToRemovedUserIds.keySet()]) {
135                if (meetingIdToRemovedUserIds.get(share.ParentId) != null) {
136                    Set<Id> removedUserIds = meetingIdToRemovedUserIds.get(share.ParentId);
137                    if (removedUserIds.contains(share.UserOrGroupId)) {
138                        shareRecordsToDelete.add(share);
139                    }
140                }
141            }

143        }

145    }

18               execute(Trigger.old);
19           }

22    void execute(List<SObject> sobjects) {        
23        if (
24            this.triggeredSobjectType == Meeting_MERC__c.sObjectType ||
25            this.triggeredSobjectType == Travel_Itinerary_MERC__c.sObjectType
26        ) {
27            MERC_TimeZoneUtility tz = new MERC_TimeZoneUtility(this.triggeredSobjectType);
28            tz.applyTimeZoneSpecificTimestamps(sobjects, null);
29        } else if (
30            this.triggeredSobjectType == Agenda_Item_MERC__c.sObjectType || 
31            this.triggeredSobjectType == Meeting_Day_MERC__c.sObjectType
32        ) {
33            MERC_TimeZoneUtility tz = new MERC_TimeZoneUtility(this.triggeredSobjectType);
34
35            Set<Id> meetingIds = new Set<Id>();
36            for (Sobject s : sobjects)
37                meetingIds.add((Id)s.get('Meeting_MERC__c'));
38
39            Map<Id,String> meetingToMeetingTimeZone = new Map<Id,String>();
40            for (Meeting_MERC__c m : [SELECT Id, Meeting_Time_Zone_MERC__c FROM Meeting_MERC__c WHERE ID in :meetingIds]) {
41                meetingToMeetingTimeZone.put(m.Id, m.Meeting_Time_Zone_MERC__c);
42            }    
43                    
44            for (Sobject s : sobjects) {
45                String meetingTimeZone = (String)meetingToMeetingTimeZone.get((Id)s.get('Meeting_MERC__c'));
46                tz.applyTimeZoneSpecificTimestamps(new List<Sobject>{s}, meetingTimeZone);
47            }
48        } 
49    }

MERC_TimeZoneUtility.cls

1/**
2 * @author Joseph Ferraro
3 *
4 * Apex class responsible for translating date/times to/from a specificed time zone/user time zone
5 */
6public with sharing class MERC_TimeZoneUtility {
7    
8    TimeZone userTimeZone = UserInfo.getTimeZone();
9    Map<String, Schema.SObjectField> fieldListMap;
10    String sobjectAPIName;
11    Map<String,String> timeZoneFieldMappings;
12    Map<String,String> stampFieldMapping;
13    List<String> timeZoneFieldsForObject;
14
15    public MERC_TimeZoneUtility(Schema.SObjectType objectType) {        
16        Schema.DescribeSObjectResult objectDescribe = objectType.getDescribe();
17        this.sobjectAPIName = objectDescribe.getName();
18
19        Schema.DescribeSObjectResult dResult = objectType.getDescribe();  
20        this.fieldListMap = dResult.fields.getMap();
21
22        this.timeZoneFieldMappings = MERC_Util.getTimeZoneFieldMapForObject(this.sobjectAPIName);
23        this.stampFieldMapping = MERC_Util.getStampFieldMapForObject(this.sobjectAPIName);
24
25        this.timeZoneFieldsForObject = this.timeZoneFieldMappings.values();
26
27        system.debug('>>>>>>>>>>> fieldListMap: '+this.fieldListMap);
28        system.debug('>>>>>>>>>>> timeZoneFieldMappings: '+timeZoneFieldMappings);
29        system.debug('>>>>>>>>>>> stampFieldMapping: '+stampFieldMapping);
30    }
31
32    //map of time zone field api name to sid: 'Meeting_Time_Zone_MERC__c' => 'America/New_York' 
33    Map<String,String> getTimeZoneFieldAPINameToTimeZoneSid(Sobject record, String timeZoneSidValueOverride) {
34        Map<String,String> timeZoneFieldAPINameToTimeZoneSid = new Map<String,String>();
35        for (String timeZoneFieldAPIName : this.timeZoneFieldsForObject) {
36            String timeZoneSid;
37            if (timeZoneSidValueOverride == null) {
38                if (record.get(timeZoneFieldAPIName) == null) continue;
39                timeZoneSid = (String)record.get(timeZoneFieldAPIName);
40            } else {
41                timeZoneSid = timeZoneSidValueOverride;
42            }
43            timeZoneSid = timeZoneSid.split('\\(')[1].replace(')','');
44            timeZoneFieldAPINameToTimeZoneSid.put(timeZoneFieldAPIName, timeZoneSid);
45        }
46
47        system.debug('>>> '+timeZoneFieldAPINameToTimeZoneSid);
48        return timeZoneFieldAPINameToTimeZoneSid;
49    }
50
51    String getFieldType(String dateOrTimeFieldApiName) {
52        Schema.SObjectField field = fieldListMap.get(dateOrTimeFieldApiName);
53        Schema.DescribeFieldResult fieldDescribe = field.getDescribe(); 
54        return String.valueOf(fieldDescribe.getSoaptype()); //DATE or DATETIME
55    }
56
57    DateTime getDateTimeValue(Sobject record, String dateOrTimeFieldApiName, String fieldType) {
58        DateTime dtValue;
59        if (fieldType == 'DATE') {
60            dtValue = Datetime.newInstance((Date)record.get(dateOrTimeFieldApiName), Time.newInstance(12, 0, 0, 0));
61        } else if (fieldType == 'DATETIME') {
62            dtValue = (DateTime)record.get(dateOrTimeFieldApiName);
63        }
64        return dtValue;
65    }
66
67    public void applyTimeZoneSpecificTimestamps(List<Sobject> sobjects, String timeZoneSidValueOverride) {
68        for (Sobject record : sobjects) {
69            system.debug('...processing object: '+record);
70            
71            Map<String,String> timeZoneFieldAPINameToTimeZoneSid = getTimeZoneFieldAPINameToTimeZoneSid(record, timeZoneSidValueOverride);
72
73            //now, for each date or date/time field, we need to calculate the UTC date and (optionally) stamp the time-zone specific value
74            for (String dateOrTimeFieldApiName : this.timeZoneFieldMappings.keySet()) { 
75                
76                system.debug('...processing: '+dateOrTimeFieldApiName); //=> Start_Time_of_Meeting_MERC__c
77                
78                if (record.get(dateOrTimeFieldApiName) == null) continue; //if the field is null, skip it
79                if (this.stampFieldMapping.get(dateOrTimeFieldApiName) == null) continue; //if the field doesn't stamp anywhere, skip it
80
81                String fieldType = getFieldType(dateOrTimeFieldApiName);
82                DateTime dtValue = getDateTimeValue(record, dateOrTimeFieldApiName, fieldType);
83                
84                //if record's value of dateOrTimeFieldApiName is null, don't bother processing
85                if (dtValue == null) continue;
86
87                //get the time zone field api name associated with this date/time
88                String associatedTimeZoneAPIName = timeZoneFieldMappings.get(dateOrTimeFieldApiName); //=> 'Meeting_Time_Zone_MERC__c'
89                if (associatedTimeZoneAPIName == null) continue;
90
91                String tzSidValueForAssociatedTimeZone = timeZoneFieldAPINameToTimeZoneSid.get(associatedTimeZoneAPIName);
92                if (tzSidValueForAssociatedTimeZone == null) continue;
93
94                system.debug('>>>> ready to stamp');
95
96                if (fieldType == 'DATE') {
97                    system.debug('>>>> field type is DATE');
98                    String fieldAPINameToStamp = this.stampFieldMapping.get(dateOrTimeFieldApiName);
99                    record.put(fieldAPINameToStamp, dtValue.date().format());
100                } else if (fieldType == 'DATETIME') {
101                    system.debug('>>>> field type is DATETIME');
102                    system.debug('>>>> ready for stamping!');
103                    String fieldAPINameToStamp = this.stampFieldMapping.get(dateOrTimeFieldApiName);
104                    String javaDateFormat = 'EEEE, dd MMM yyyy HH:mm z';
105                    //String javaDateFormat = 'EEE, d MMM yyyy HH:mm, zzzz';
106                    system.debug('>>>> stamping field: '+fieldAPINameToStamp);
107                    system.debug('>>>> stamping value: '+dtValue.format(javaDateFormat, tzSidValueForAssociatedTimeZone));
108
109                    record.put(fieldAPINameToStamp, dtValue.format(javaDateFormat, tzSidValueForAssociatedTimeZone));
110                }
111            }
112        }
113    }

115    public void convertDateTimes(list<Sobject> sobjects, Boolean setDateTimesAccordingToUserLocal) {

117    }
118
119    public void convertDateTimes(List<Sobject> sobjects, Boolean setDateTimesAccordingToUserLocal, String timeZoneSidValueOverride) {        
120
121        for (Sobject record : sobjects) {
122            system.debug('...processing object: '+record);
123            
124            Map<String,String> timeZoneFieldAPINameToTimeZoneSid = getTimeZoneFieldAPINameToTimeZoneSid(record, timeZoneSidValueOverride);
125
126            //now, for each date or date/time field, we need to calculate the UTC date and (optionally) stamp the time-zone specific value
127            for (String dateOrTimeFieldApiName : timeZoneFieldMappings.keySet()) { 
128                system.debug('...processing: '+dateOrTimeFieldApiName);
129                //dateOrTimeFieldApiName = 'Start_Time_of_Meeting_MERC__c'
130                
131                try {
132                    if (record.get(dateOrTimeFieldApiName) == null) continue;
133                } catch(System.SObjectException e) {
134                    continue;
135                }
136                
137                String fieldType = getFieldType(dateOrTimeFieldApiName);
138                DateTime dtValue = getDateTimeValue(record, dateOrTimeFieldApiName, fieldType);
139                
140                //if record's value of dateOrTimeFieldApiName is null, don't bother processing
141                if (dtValue == null) continue;
142
143                //get the time zone field api name associated with this date/time
144                String associatedTimeZoneAPIName = timeZoneFieldMappings.get(dateOrTimeFieldApiName); //=> 'Meeting_Time_Zone_MERC__c'
145                if (associatedTimeZoneAPIName == null) continue;
146
147                String tzSidValueForAssociatedTimeZone = timeZoneFieldAPINameToTimeZoneSid.get(associatedTimeZoneAPIName);
148                if (tzSidValueForAssociatedTimeZone == null) continue;
149
150                TimeZone associatedTimeZoneValue = TimeZone.getTimeZone(tzSidValueForAssociatedTimeZone);
151
152                Integer userGmtOffset = userTimeZone.getOffset(dtValue); //gets user's offset to gmt
153                Integer associatedFieldGmtOffset = associatedTimeZoneValue.getOffset(dtValue); //gets meeting's offset to gmt
154                system.debug('>>>> '+userGmtOffset);
155                system.debug('>>>> '+associatedFieldGmtOffset);
156                
157                Integer correction;
158                if (setDateTimesAccordingToUserLocal) {
159                    correction = userGmtOffset - associatedFieldGmtOffset;
160                } else {
161                    correction = associatedFieldGmtOffset - userGmtOffset;
162                }
163                
164                DateTime correctedDateTime = dtValue.addMinutes(correction / (1000 * 60));
165
166                system.debug('>>>> ready to convert date/times');
167
168                if (fieldType == 'DATE') {
169                    system.debug('>>>> field type is DATE');
170                    record.put(dateOrTimeFieldApiName, correctedDateTime.date());
171                } else if (fieldType == 'DATETIME') {
172                    system.debug('>>>> field type is DATETIME');
173                    system.debug('>>>> setting field: '+dateOrTimeFieldApiName);
174                    system.debug('>>>> setting to: '+correctedDateTime);
175                    record.put(dateOrTimeFieldApiName, correctedDateTime);
176                }
177            }
178        }
179
180    }

38    void calculateHotelTov(List<SObject> sobjects) {
39        if (
40            (
41                this.triggeredSobjectType == Meeting_Vendor_MERC__c.SobjectType || 
42                this.triggeredSobjectType == Travel_Itinerary_MERC__c.SobjectType
43            ) 
44            && Trigger.isAfter
45        ) {
46            Set<Id> meetingIds = new Set<Id>();
47            
48            //check for room rate change
49            if (this.triggeredSobjectType == Meeting_Vendor_MERC__c.SobjectType) {
50                for (Meeting_Vendor_MERC__c vendor : (List<Meeting_Vendor_MERC__c>)sobjects) {
51                    if (Trigger.oldMap.get(vendor.Id).get('Room_Rate_MERC__c') != vendor.Room_Rate_MERC__c &&
52                        vendor.Meeting_Status_MERC__c != 'Completed' &&
53                        vendor.Meeting_Status_MERC__c != 'Cancelled') {
54                        //room rate has changed
55                        meetingIds.add(vendor.Meeting_MERC__c);
56                    }
57                }    
58
59            //check for meeting vendor change
60            //TODO: we don't need to process all meetings, so proide list of affected tavel itineraries instead
61            } else if (this.triggeredSobjectType == Travel_Itinerary_MERC__c.SobjectType) {
62                for (Travel_Itinerary_MERC__c ti : (List<Travel_Itinerary_MERC__c>)sobjects) {
63                    if (Trigger.oldMap.get(ti.Id).get('Meeting_Vendor_MERC__c') != ti.Meeting_Vendor_MERC__c &&

65                        ti.Meeting_Status_MERC__c != 'Cancelled') {

69                }
70            }            
71
72            if (meetingIds.size() == 0) return;
73
74            Map<Id, Meeting_Day_MERC__c> meetingDays = new Map<Id, Meeting_Day_MERC__c>([SELECT ID, Date_MERC__c FROM Meeting_Day_MERC__c WHERE Meeting_MERC__c in :meetingIds]);

129    public static String generateRandomString(Integer count) {
130        String chars = '0123456789ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXTZabcdefghiklmnopqrstuvwxyz';
131        String hash = '';
132        for (integer i = 0; i < count; i++) {
133            Integer rnum = Math.floor(Math.random() * chars.length()).intValue();
134            hash += chars.substring(rnum,rnum+1);
135        }
136        return hash;
137    }

233            }

277    public PageReference createAccount() {
278        removeAccountError = false;
279        didInsertSucceed = false;
280        didTryCreate = true;
281
282        if(createAccount.RecordTypeId == null) {
283            ApexPages.addMessage(new ApexPages.Message(ApexPages.Severity.Error, System.Label.Create_Person_Record_Type_Required_MVN));
284            return null;
285        }
286
287        //Creation
288        SavePoint sp = Database.setSavePoint();
289
290        try {
291            if(!String.isBlank(createAccount.Phone)) {
292                createAccount.Phone = createAccount.Phone.replaceAll('[^0-9]', '');
293            }
294            if(!String.isBlank(createAccount.Fax)) {
295                createAccount.Fax = createAccount.Fax.replaceAll('[^0-9]', '');
296            }
297            if(createAccount.PersonEmail != null && createAccount.PersonEmail != '' && !Pattern.matches('([a-zA-Z0-9_\\-\\.]+)@((\\[a-z]{1,3}\\.[a-z]{1,3}\\.[a-z]{1,3}\\.)|(([a-zA-Z0-9\\-]+\\.)+))([a-zA-Z]{2,4}|[0-9]{1,3})', createAccount.PersonEmail)){
298                ApexPages.addMessage(new ApexPages.message(ApexPages.severity.Error, Label.Invalid_Email_Address_MVN));
299                return null;
300            }
301            
302            insert createAccount;
303            
304            createAddress.Account_GLBL__c = createAccount.Id;
305
306            if((createAddress.Name != null && !String.isBlank(createAddress.Name))
307                || (createAddress.Line_2_Adrs_Txt_GLBL__c != null && !String.isBlank(createAddress.Line_2_Adrs_Txt_GLBL__c))
308                || (createAddress.City_GLBL__c != null && !String.isBlank(createAddress.City_GLBL__c))
309                || (createAddress.St_Cd_GLBL__c != null && !String.isBlank(createAddress.St_Cd_GLBL__c))){
310                insert createAddress;
311            }
312            
313            if(!standAloneSearch){
314                if(!createReferredBy){
315                    cs.AccountId = createAccount.Id;
316                    cs.Address_GLBL__c = createAddress.Id;
317                    cs.Account_Fax_GLBL__c = createAccount.Fax;
318                    cs.Account_Phone_GLBL__c = createAccount.Phone;
319                    cs.Account_Email_GLBL__c = createAccount.PersonEmail;
320                }else{
321                    cs.Referred_By_GLBL__c = createAccount.Id;
322                }
323                
324                createReferredBy = false;
325
326                update cs;
327                getCaseValues();
328            }
329
330            clearSearch();
331            
332            didInsertSucceed = true;
333        }
334        catch (Exception e) {
335            //need to clone failed account and address records to clear id field
336            createAccount = createAccount.clone(false,true,false,false);
337            createAddress = createAddress.clone(false,true,false,false);
338            getCaseValues();
339            
340            ApexPages.addMessages(e);
341            Database.rollback(sp);
342        }
343        return null;
344    }

359    public PageReference doSearch(){
360        removeAccountError = false;
361        
362        searchAccount.FirstName = searchAccount.FirstName != null ? (searchAccount.FirstName.length() > 0 ? String.escapeSingleQuotes(searchAccount.FirstName.trim()) : '') : '';
363        searchAccount.LastName = searchAccount.LastName != null ? (searchAccount.LastName.length() > 0 ? String.escapeSingleQuotes(searchAccount.LastName.trim()) : '') : '';
364        searchAccount.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c = searchAccount.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c != null ? (searchAccount.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c.length() > 0 ? String.escapeSingleQuotes(searchAccount.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c.trim()) : '') : '';
365        searchAccount.Phone = searchAccount.Phone != null ? (searchAccount.Phone.length() > 0 ? String.escapeSingleQuotes(searchAccount.Phone.trim()) : '') : '';
366        searchAddress.City_GLBL__c = searchAddress.City_GLBL__c != null ? (searchAddress.City_GLBL__c.length() > 0 ? String.escapeSingleQuotes(searchAddress.City_GLBL__c.trim()) : '') : '';
367        searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c = searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c != null ? (searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c.length() > 0 ? String.escapeSingleQuotes(searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c.trim()) : '') : '';
368        
369        searchResults = new List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
370        
371        //Make sure something is filled out
372        didTryCreate = false;
373        if (String.isBlank(searchAccount.FirstName) && String.isBlank(searchAccount.LastName) && String.isBlank(searchAccount.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c) && String.isBlank(searchAccount.Phone) && String.isBlank(searchAddress.City_GLBL__c) && String.isBlank(searchAddress.St_Cd_GLBL__c) && String.isBlank(searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c)) {
374            ApexPages.addMessage(new ApexPages.Message(ApexPages.Severity.Info, System.Label.Search_Term_Required_MVN));
375            return null;
376        }
377
378        //Pick search path: Only Accounts, Addresses, SOSL Phone
379        if (!String.isBlank(searchAccount.Phone)) {
380            searchResults = buildPhoneSearchResults();
381        } else if (String.isBlank(searchAddress.City_GLBL__c) && String.isBlank(searchAddress.St_Cd_GLBL__c) && String.isBlank(searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c)) {
382            searchResults = buildAccountSearchResults();
383        } else {
384            searchResults = buildAddressSearchResults();
385        }
386
387        if(searchResults == null) {
388            searchResults = new List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
389            return null;
390        }
391
392        if (searchResults.size() >= SEARCHLIMIT) {
393            searchResults = new List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
394            ApexPages.addMessage(new ApexPages.Message(ApexPages.Severity.Info, System.Label.Too_Many_Results_MVN));
395        } else if (searchResults.size() == 0 ) {
396            searchResults = new List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
397            ApexPages.addMessage(new ApexPages.Message(ApexPages.Severity.Info, System.Label.No_Search_Results_MVN));
398        }
399
400        if(searchResults == null) searchResults = new List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
401        didSearch = true;
402        showNewButton = true;
403        return null;
404    }

406    public List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN> buildAddressSearchResults() {
407        List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN> resultList = new List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
408        String qString = 'SELECT ' + ADDRESSFIELDS;
409        qString += ' FROM Address_GLBL__c ' + buildAddressWhereClause() + ADDRESSORDERBY + ' LIMIT ' + SEARCHLIMIT;
410
411        List<Address_GLBL__c> addressList = database.query(qString);
412        for(Address_GLBL__c a : addressList) {
413                Account acct = new Account(Id = a.Account_GLBL__c);
414                acct.FirstName = a.Account_GLBL__r.FirstName;
415                acct.LastName = a.Account_GLBL__r.LastName;
416                acct.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c = a.Account_GLBL__r.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c;
417                acct.RecordTypeId = a.Account_GLBL__r.RecordTypeId;
418    
419                resultList.add(new PersonSearchResultMockMVN(acct,a));
420        }
421        
422        return resultList;
423    }

425    public List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN> buildAccountSearchResults() {
426        List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN> resultList = new List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
427
428        String qString = 'SELECT ' + ACCOUNTFIELDS;
429        qString += ',(SELECT ' + ADDRESSFIELDS + ' FROM Addresses_GLBL__r)';
430        qString += ' FROM Account ' + buildAccountWhereClause() + ACCOUNTORDERBY + ' LIMIT ' + SEARCHLIMIT;
431        system.debug(qString);
432        system.debug(validRecordTypeIds);
433        String translatedCountryValue = null;
434        if(searchAddress.Adrs_Cntry_Cd_GLBL__c != null && searchAddress.Adrs_Cntry_Cd_GLBL__c != ''){
435            for(Schema.PicklistEntry countryPicklistVal:Schema.sObjectType.Address_GLBL__c.fields.Adrs_Cntry_Cd_GLBL__c.getPicklistValues()){
436                if(countryPicklistVal.getValue() == searchAddress.Adrs_Cntry_Cd_GLBL__c){
437                    translatedCountryValue = countryPicklistVal.getLabel();
438                }
439            }
440        }
441        
442        List<Account> accountList = database.query(qString);
443        for(Account a : accountList ) {
444            if(a.Addresses_GLBL__r.size() > 0) {
445                for(Address_GLBL__c addr : a.Addresses_GLBL__r) {
446                    if(translatedCountryValue != null &&
447                        translatedCountryValue != addr.Adrs_Cntry_Cd_GLBL__c){
448                        continue;
449                    }
450                    resultList.add(new PersonSearchResultMockMVN(a,addr));
451                }
452            } else {
453                resultList.add(new PersonSearchResultMockMVN(a));
454            }
455        }
456
457        return resultList;
458    }

460    public List<PersonSearchResultMockMVN> buildPhoneSearchResults () {
461
462        //Do initial query
463        String queryString = buildSOSLString();
464        if(queryString == null) {
465            return null;
466        }
467
468        LIST<LIST<SObject>> soslResult;
469        try {
470            system.debug('>>>>>>> ' + queryString);
471            soslResult = search.query(queryString);
472        } catch (exception e) {
473            ApexPages.addMessage(new ApexPages.Message(ApexPages.Severity.Info, e.getMessage()));
474            return null;
475        }
476
477        //Set up Maps and lists needed
478        LIST<LIST<SObject>> results = soslResult;
479        List<Account> acctResults = new List<Account>();
480        List<Address_GLBL__c> addrResults = new List<Address_GLBL__c>();
481        //AccountId_AddressId to the Mock Result
482        Map<String,PersonSearchResultMockMVN> uResults = new Map<String,PersonSearchResultMockMVN>();
483        
484        Map<Id,Account> acctIds = new Map<Id,Account>();
485
486        //Separate out what kind each list is
487        for(List<SObject> oneKind : results) {
488            if(oneKind.size() > 0) {
489                String typeId = oneKind[0].Id;
490                if(typeId.startsWith(acctPrefix)) {
491                    acctResults = (List<Account>) oneKind;
492                } else if(typeId.startsWith(addrPrefix)) {
493                    addrResults = (List<Address_GLBL__c>) oneKind;
494                }
495            }
496        }
497
498        //Get related Addresses
499        for(Account a : acctResults) {
500            acctIds.put(a.Id,a);
501            if (String.isBlank(searchAddress.City_GLBL__c) && String.isBlank(searchAddress.St_Cd_GLBL__c) && String.isBlank(searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c)) {
502                uResults.put(a.Id,new PersonSearchResultMockMVN(a));
503            }
504        }
505
506        Set<Id> idSet = acctIds.keySet();
507        String qString = 'SELECT ' + ADDRESSFIELDS + ' FROM Address_GLBL__c ' + buildAddressWhereClause() + ' AND Account_GLBL__c in :idSet' + ADDRESSORDERBY + ' LIMIT ' + SEARCHLIMIT;
508        List<Address_GLBL__c> subAddrs = database.query(qString);
509        addrResults.addAll(subAddrs);
510
511        for(Address_GLBL__c addr : addrResults) {
512            Account acct = new Account(Id = addr.Account_GLBL__c);
513            acct.FirstName = addr.Account_GLBL__r.FirstName;
514            acct.LastName = addr.Account_GLBL__r.LastName;
515            acct.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c = addr.Account_GLBL__r.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c;
516            acct.RecordTypeId = addr.Account_GLBL__r.RecordTypeId;
517
518            String key = acct.Id + '_' + addr.Id;
519            if (!uResults.containsKey(key)) {
520                if(uResults.containsKey(acct.Id)) {
521                    PersonSearchResultMockMVN psr = uResults.remove(acct.Id);
522                    psr.setAddress(addr);
523                    uResults.put(key,psr);
524                } else {
525                    uResults.put(key,new PersonSearchResultMockMVN(acct,addr));
526                }
527            }
528        }
529
530        return uResults.values();
531    }
532
533    public String buildSOSLString(){
534        //Put together final query and error check it
535        String qString = 'FIND {';
536        String findString = '';
537
538        //Cannot search for phone numbers with punctuation
539        findString = searchAccount.Phone.replaceAll('[^0-9]', '');
540        if (findString.length() < 2) {
541            ApexPages.addMessage(new ApexPages.Message(ApexPages.Severity.Info, System.Label.SOSL_Phone_Search_Min_Char_MVN + ' ' + findString));
542            return null;
543        }
544
545        qString += findString + '} IN PHONE FIELDS RETURNING ';
546        qString += ' Address_GLBL__c (' + ADDRESSFIELDS;
547        qString += buildAddressWhereClause();
548        qString += ADDRESSORDERBY;
549        qString += '), ';
550        qString += ' Account (' + ACCOUNTFIELDS;
551        qString += buildAccountWhereClause();
552        qString += ACCOUNTORDERBY;
553        qString += ') ';
554
555        return qString;
556    }
557
558    public String buildAccountWhereClause() {
559        String acctString = '';
560        acctString +=' WHERE IsDeleted = false ';
561
562        Map<String,String> fieldMap = new Map<String,String>();
563        fieldMap.put('LastName like',searchAccount.LastName);
564        fieldMap.put('FirstName like',searchAccount.FirstName);
565        fieldMap.put('Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c like',searchAccount.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c);
566
567        for(String field : fieldMap.keySet()) {
568            String sTerm = fieldMap.get(field);
569            if(sTerm != null && !String.isBlank(sTerm)){
570                acctString += ' AND (' + field + ' \'' + sTerm.replaceAll('\\*', '%') + '\')';
571            }
572        }
573
574        if(recordTypeText == 'All') {
575            acctString += ' AND (RecordTypeId in :validRecordTypeIds)';
576        } else {
577            acctString += ' AND (RecordTypeId = \'' + recordTypeText + '\')';
578        }
579
580        return acctString;
581    }
582
583    public String buildAddressWhereClause() {
584        String addrString = ' WHERE IsDeleted = false ';
585
586        Map<String,String> fieldMap = new Map<String,String>();
587        fieldMap.put('City_GLBL__c like',searchAddress.City_GLBL__c);
588        fieldMap.put('St_Cd_GLBL__c =',searchAddress.St_Cd_GLBL__c);
589        fieldMap.put('Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c like',searchAddress.Zip_Postal_Code_GLBL__c);
590        fieldMap.put('Adrs_Cntry_Cd_GLBL__c =',searchAddress.Adrs_Cntry_Cd_GLBL__c);
591        fieldMap.put('Account_GLBL__r.LastName like',searchAccount.LastName);
592        fieldMap.put('Account_GLBL__r.FirstName like',searchAccount.FirstName);
593        fieldMap.put('Account_GLBL__r.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c like',searchAccount.Mdl_Nm_GLBL__c);
594
595        for(String field : fieldMap.keySet()) {
596            String sTerm = fieldMap.get(field);
597            if(sTerm != null && !String.isBlank(sTerm)){
598                addrString += ' AND (' + field + ' \'' + sTerm.replaceAll('\\*', '%') + '\')';
599            }
600        }
601
